comments_experiment: Control conditions and high food level. Larvae from the high food level received ad libitum Artemia nauplii six days a week. After moulting into the final instar, larvae additionally were fed three chironomids three times a week

food_type: Adult butterflies were fed with artificial nectar provided through artificial flowers

comments_experiment: Maintenance temperature was probably between 18 degrees (during winter) and 28 degrees (during summer)
Two week temperature shift from maintenance 10C administered 13 weeks after start of the Experiment
